snippet.title: Grippy Golf — Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
✨Wishlist Grippy Golf!!✨
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2299080?utm_source=youtube

Grippy Golf is a speedrunning platformer where obstacles stick to the ball!  Launch yourself across the course, gathering an ever-growing cluster of objects as you aim for a hole in one!
